tactic: induction alpha as [alpha IH|alpha IH|]; try (intro H; inversion H).
exceptions.exn: Expects a disjunctive pattern with 2 branches.

original: induction alpha as [alpha IH|alpha IH|]; try (intro H; inversion H). intro H; inversion H; destruct H0 as [beta]; destruct H2 as [gamma]. apply (IH beta); exists gamma; auto.
